name: LivingEvent.LivingJumpEvent
description: LivingJumpEvent is fired when an Entity jumps. This event is fired whenever an Entity jumps in LivingEntity#jumpFromGround() , MagmaCube#jumpFromGround() , Slime#jumpFromGround() , Camel#executeRidersJump() , and AbstractHorse#executeRidersJump() . This event is fired via the CommonHooks.onLivingJump(LivingEntity) . This event is not ICancellableEvent . This event does not have a result. invalid reference HasResult This event is fired on the NeoForge.EVENT_BUS .
